        "a": "Yes. Google stopped accepting new developer signups for the Google Fit REST and Android APIs on 1 May 2024, and has said support runs only until the end of 2026 (verify the exact turndown date against Google's official docs). Existing integrations keep working until then, but no new projects can be created."
